short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: DM allows users of pump.fun to chat with each other in real time

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
DM is a light social networking extension that allows users to chat with other users who are also on pump.fun.

Users can chat and send celebration fireworks to each other.

I hope you enjoy the app and please provide me with feedback.
